snippet.title: Phoenix Wright: Legal Panels - 3.5 Remastered
snippet.description:
A trailer for the remastered 3.5 version of Phoenix Wright: Legal Panels, a custom crossover Ace Attorney fangame. This update adds additional effects, a fully arranged soundtrack, more plot details, time and space resets, and more.

The game can be downloaded and played on Court Records at http://forums.court-records.net/viewtopic.php?f=36&t=31675.

Let there be glory for Team Galactic!
